'Yan majalisar dokokin Wales na tsoron cewa za su shiga cikin wasan kwaikwayon Muppet Show
Wasu 'yan majalisa sun amince da shawarar da aka yi na canza sunayensu zuwa MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
An yi wannan gargadi ne bayan an ce za a kira Majalisar ta 'Yan majalisar dokokin Wales.
Yanzu, 'yan majalisa daga bangarori daban-daban na siyasa suna tsoron cewa sabon taken zai sa su zama abin dariya.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Labour ya ce jam'iyyarsa na fargabar cewa sabon sunan zai yi karin magana akan kalmomin Twp da Pwp.
Don masu karatu da ba 'yan Wales ba, a yaren Welsh, twp yana nufin mai ƙwarewa, kuma pwp yana nufin kuraje.
Wani dan jam'iyyar Plaid ya ce jam'iyyar ba ta gamsu da wannan batu ba, don haka za su ba da shawarwari.
Wani dan majalisa mai ra'ayin mazan jiya ya ce jam'iyyarsa ta bude baki ga sauya sunan, duk da haka ya lura cewa kawai tsalle ne daga MWP zuwa Muppet.
Abin lura shi ne, a yaren Welsh, ana furta w kamar yadda ake furta u a yaren Yorkshire, wato MWP a matsayin map.
Kwamitin Majalisar Dokokin kasar da ke da alhakin tsara dokar da za ta sauya sunan majalisar ya ce: A game da lakabi da za a yi wa 'yan majalisar, a bayyane yake cewa 'yan majalisar ne za su yanke shawara ta karshe.
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba da damar Majalisar Wakilai ta canza sunan.
A watan Yuni, Hukumar ta wallafa sakamakon wani bincike da aka yi da ya nuna cewa an amince da sunan majalisar Wales.
Game da taken 'yan majalisa, Hukumar ta fi son taken Welsh Parliament Member da kuma WMP, amma an fi son madadin MWP a cikin taron jama'a.
'Yan majalisar sun ci gaba da kawo sabbin hanyoyin, amma cimma yarjejeniya na da matukar wahala, wanda hakan ke haifar da damuwa ga shugaban majalisar Elin Jones, wacce za ta gabatar da kudurin dokar sauya sunan a makonni masu zuwa.
A cewarsa, dokar ta shafi tsarin majalisar dokoki da kuma tsarin gudanar da ayyukanta.
