Bidiyo: Dan wasan Liverpool Daniel Sturridge ya zura kwallo mai kyau a wasan Chelsea
A wasan farko na gasar Premier a Stamford Bridge a London, Daniel Sturridge ya ci Liverpool a minti na 89 kuma ya ceci Liverpool daga shan kashi a hannun Chelsea.
Tawagarsa ta ci 0-1 lokacin da Sturridge ya ci kwallo daga Xherdan Shaqiri a nisan mita 30 daga kofar Chelsea.
Da farko ya jefa kwallon zuwa hagu, sannan ya buga ta da babbar kwallo a cikin kusurwar ƙofar.
Harbin ya tashi sama da goma sha shida, kuma raga ya tashi zuwa saman dama.
Daga karshe kwallon ta kai raga a saman Kepa Arrizabalaga da ke buga kwallo.
"Ina so in samu matsayi ne kawai, domin akwai wani kamar Shaq da ke ci gaba da buga kwallon, don haka na yi kokarin sanya kaina a matsayin mafi kyau", Sturridge ya ce a cikin amsa ga LiverpoolFC.com.
Na ga Kante yana zuwa, sai na kashe shi, kuma ban yi tunani sosai ba, sai na harbe shi.
Chelsea ta ci gaba da ci 1-0 a rabin lokaci bayan da ta ci kwallo ta dan wasan Belgium, Eden Hazard a minti na 25.
Matteo Kovacic ya buga kwallo a tsakiya na tsakiya kuma ya shiga filin Liverpool.
Kovacic ya yi saurin buga kwallo, sai ya sake buga kwallon a tsakiyar filin wasa.
