Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sauraron Brett Kavanaugh
A cikin gidajen talabijin shida, mutane sama da miliyan 20 sun kalli shaidar Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ke neman zama babban alkalin kotun koli da kuma Christine Blasey Ford, wadda ta zarge shi da fyade a shekarun 1980.
A halin yanzu, harkar siyasa ba ta tashi ba, kuma an tilasta wa masu watsa shirye-shirye dakatar da shirin a ranar Juma'a saboda wani rikici na karshe: Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya yi nasarar ba FBI mako guda don bincika tuhumar.
Ford ya shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai cewa ya tabbata cewa a lokacin wani biki a makarantar sakandare, ya kama Kavanaugh kuma ya yi ƙoƙarin tuɓe shi.
Kavanaugh ya shaida cewa ya tabbata cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Wataƙila mutane fiye da miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli shaidar a ranar Juma'a fiye da yadda Nielsen ta ruwaito.
Nielsen ya ƙididdige yawan masu kallo na CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Sauran tashoshin da suka watsa wannan sauraron, kamar PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network ba su da samuwa.
Bugu da ƙari, Nielsen yana da wuya a auna yawan mutanen da ke kallon shirye-shiryen a wuraren aiki.
Don kwatanta, wannan shi ne yawan masu kallo da ake samu a wasan kwallon kafa ko kuma a bikin Oscar.
A cewar Nielsen, Fox News Channel, wanda ke nuna masu goyon bayan Kavanaugh, shi ne mafi yawan masu kallo, wanda ya kai kimanin miliyan 5.69 a duk tsawon ranar.
A na biyu, ABC tana da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS ta samu rabon kallo 3.1, NBC ta samu rabon kallo 2.94, MSNBC ta samu rabon kallo 2.89, kuma CNN ta samu rabon kallo miliyan 2.52 a cewar rahoton Nielsen.
Ba a daina nuna sha'awar ba bayan an yi masa tambayoyi.
Babban jarumin wasan kwaikwayon na ranar Juma'a shi ne Sanata Flake.
Bayan da ofishin Sanata Kavanaugh ya fitar da sanarwar cewa zai kada kuri'arsa, a safiyar ranar Juma'a, CNN da CBS sun nuna shi a cikin taron masu zanga-zanga suna maraba da shi yayin da yake kokarin shiga cikin lif don halartar taron kwamitin shari'a.
Ya tsaya yana kuka na mintoci kaɗan yayin da taron suka yi masa baƙar magana kuma CNN ta watsa shi kai tsaye.
"Ina tsaye a gabanka", wata mata ta gaya wa Sanatan.
Shin kana ganin Kavanaugh yana faɗin gaskiya a gaban jama'ar ƙasar?
Mutane da yawa suka yi ihu, "Kai ne wanda ya yi abin da ba mace ba ta yi ba".
Flake ya ce ofishinsa ya ba da sanarwa, kuma kafin a rufe ƙofar lif ɗin, ya ce zai ba da labarinsa a lokacin sauraron kwamiti.
Sa'o'i bayan haka, an watsa shirye-shiryen talabijin da na talabijin a kai tsaye yayin da kwamitin ya kada kuri'ar ko za a gabatar da takarar Kavanaugh ga majalisar dattijai.
Sai dai Flake ya ce zai amince da hakan ne idan FBI ta fara binciken zargin da ake yi wa dan takarar a mako mai zuwa kamar yadda 'yan Democrat suka bukaci.
Flake ya tabbatar da bukatar hakan bayan tattaunawar da yayi da abokinsa, Sanata Chris Coons, dan jam'iyyar Democrat.
Flake ya yanke shawarar ne bayan ya tattauna da Coons da wasu sanatoci.
Flake ya yi amfani da ikonsa da kyau, domin babu shakka idan ba a gudanar da bincike ba, 'yan Republican ba za su sami kuri'un da ake bukata ba don amincewa da takarar Kavanaugh.
Shugaba Trump ya kaddamar da binciken FBI kan zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh.
