A matsayin sabon shiga gasar Premier, Livingston ya ba Rangers mamaki sosai ta hanyar cin nasararsa ta biyu a kan Steven Gerrard, wanda ya yi wasa 18 a matsayin kocin kungiyar ta Ibrox.
Golan Dolly Menga ya kawo canji, saboda Gary Holt da Hibernian sun shiga gasar neman gurbin biyu.
A yau Lahadi, Gerrard zai kara da Hearts, wanda ke kan gaba a gasar.
Amma kafin wannan, Rangers za ta kara da Rapid Wien a gasar cin kofin Turai ranar Alhamis.
A halin yanzu Livingston ta kara nasara a gasar cin kofin duniya da ta yi da ta ci shida, wanda ke nufin Holt wanda ya maye gurbin Kenny Miller a watan jiya bai samu nasarar zama a tawagar ba.
Livingston ta rasa abubuwa da dama da ta yi da 'yan wasan da ba su yi wasa daidai ba
Kungiyar Holt ta iya samun ci gaba tun kafin ta ci kwallo daya a wasan, saboda sun yi wa Rangers matsala da wasansu na gaba.
Scott Robinson ya shiga cikin tsaron abokan hamayyarsa amma ya dauki lokaci mai tsawo yana kaiwa, sai kuma Alan Lithgow ya yi kokarin kaiwa gaba bayan ya yi tsalle don ya kai ga Craig Halkett wanda ya yi tsalle a gaban layin.
'Yan wasan gida sun bar Rangers su yi wasan nasu, saboda sun tabbata cewa za su iya damun baƙi a cikin yanayin wasan da aka yi rikodin.
Wannan ƙwallo mai muhimmanci ya fito ne daga irin wannan yanayi.
Rangers sun samu damar buga kwallo, Livingston ya samu damar buga kwallo, Declan Gallagher da Robinson sun samar da wani yanayi ga Menga, wanda ya yi amfani da wannan damar ya buga daga tsakiyar raga ta 16.
A wannan lokacin wasan Rangers sun jagoranci kwallon, amma har yanzu tsaron gida ya kasance mai ƙarfi, kuma ƙofar Liam Kelly ba ta da wata matsala.
Wannan yanayin ya ci gaba a rabi na biyu na wasan, sai dai a wani lokaci da Kelly ya kare Alfredo Morelos.
Dan wasan Rangers Allan McGregor ya yi wa Scott Pittman doki, sannan Lithgow ya rasa wata hanyar daga Livingston.
An ci gaba da samun kwallaye a cikin Livingston ta 16, amma masu karewa sun kauce wa kowane lokaci.
Wani wasa mai ban mamaki  daga Livingston  nazarin wasan
A tashar Tony Macaroni Arena, muna kawo muku Alasdair Lamont, wakilin BBC Scotland.
Livingston ya yi aiki sosai kuma ya ba da gudummawa sosai.
'Yan wasan sun yi fice sosai, kuma sun wuce dukan abin da aka ce.
Ko da yake 'yan wasan da kuma yadda suke wasa ba su canza ba tun lokacin da suka dawo a kan gaba, amma kokarin Holt ya cancanci yabo, saboda kocin ya sa tawagar ta yi farin ciki tun lokacin da ya zo.
Wasu 'yan wasa sun yi nasara a wasan.
Halkett ya zama babban jami'in tsaro tare da kyakkyawan tsari, kuma Menga ya ba Connor Goldson da Joe Worrall izza sosai.
Rangers sun yi wasa ba tare da wani ra'ayi ba.
Duk da cewa sun yi aiki sosai a wasu lokatai a karkashin Gerrard, amma ba su iya yin hakan ba.
A duk lokacin da aka yi wasa da kwallon kafa, sai da aka yi amfani da shi wajen buga wasan karshe.
An yi maraba da Erdogan a birnin Cologne
An yi farin ciki da farin ciki a taron shugabannin Turkiyya da Jamus da suka yi a safiyar Asabar (29 ga Satumba) a Berlin.
Wannan ita ce rana ta karshe da Erdoğan ya kai ziyarar raba gardama a Jamus, da nufin inganta dangantaka tsakanin kasashen NATO.
Dangantaka tsakanin kasashen biyu ta tabarbare ne saboda batutuwan da suka shafi 'yancin bil adama, 'yancin yada labarai da kuma kasancewar Turkiyya a cikin EU.
Erdogan ya ci gaba da tafiya zuwa Cologne don bikin buɗe sabon masallaci mai girma.
Birnin Cologne yana da gida ga mafi yawan al'ummar Turkawa a waje da Turkiyya.
'Yan sanda sun haramta taron mutane 25,000 a gaban masallacin saboda dalilai na tsaro, amma magoya bayan shugaban sun zo don ganin shugaban Turkiyya.
Bugu da kari, daruruwan masu zanga-zangar adawa da Erdogan  da dama daga cikinsu Kurdawa  sun nuna rashin jin dadin su game da manufofin Erdogan da kuma yadda gwamnatin Jamus ta amince da karbar shugaban.
Wannan zanga-zangar ta nuna yadda shugaban kasar ke raba kan jama'a, wasu 'yan asalin Turkiyya na Jamus suna masa murna a matsayin gwarzo, wasu kuma suna ganin shi mai mulkin kama karya ne.
