Trump ya ce Kavanaugh ya sha wahala daga rashin amincewa da kuma fushin jam'iyyar Democrat
"Duk wanda ya zabi Kavanaugh zai zabi adawa da mummunan aiki da kuma mummunan aiki na jam'iyyar Democrat", in ji Trump a wani taron da aka yi a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Trump ya ce Kavanaugh ya sha wahala daga rashin amincewa da 'yan jam'iyyar Democrat a lokacin da ya nemi takara.
Kavanaugh ya shaida a gaban majalisa a ranar Alhamis inda ya musanta da karfi da kuma sha'awar da Christine Blasey Ford ta yi cewa ya yi mata fyade shekaru da dama da suka gabata a matsayin matashi.
A wannan lokacin, Ford ya shaida kuma ya goyi bayan abin da ya fada.
A ranar Asabar, shugaban ya ce jama'ar Amurka sun ga da idanunsu irin halayyar Kavanaugh mai ban mamaki da kuma karfin hali.
"Zaɓen da na yi wa Alkalin Kavanaugh, na yi ne ga ɗaya daga cikin manyan lauyoyi na zamaninmu, wanda ke da kyakkyawan tarihin aikin gwamnati",
Shugaban ya yi magana a kan takarar Kavanaugh a lokacin da yake magana game da muhimmancin kada kuri'un Republican a zaben.
Muna da makonni biyar kafin mu yanke shawara mafi muhimmanci a rayuwarmu.
Ni kaina ba zan yi takara ba, amma a zahiri zan yi takara, in ji shi.
Saboda haka, zan je duk inda zan iya don tallafawa 'yan takarar da suka fi dacewa.
Trump ya yi jayayya cewa 'yan Democrat suna amfani da dabarun tsayayya da hanawa.
Ana sa ran za a fara kada kuri'ar neman takarar Kavanaugh a majalisar dattijai a ranar Juma'a, a cewar wani babban mai ba da shawara kan jam'iyyar Republican.
