Ya yi da'awar cewa rashin aikin yi da rashin ilimi su ne manyan abubuwan da ke sa matasa su shiga cikin ƙungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda.
Ya kamata Amurka ta ninka kudaden da take bayarwa don samar da hanyoyin samar da na'urar kere kere.
Yayin da kasar Sin ke kara samun himma wajen bincike da ci gaban fasaha, Amurka ta kamata ta ninka tallafin da take baiwa wannan fasaha, in ji Kai-Fu Lee, mai saka jari da kuma amfani da fasaha, wanda ya taba aiki da Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Ya ce hakan ne bayan da gwamnatin Amurka ta yi wasu sanarwa game da fasaha ta wucin gadi duk da cewa Amurka ba ta da wata dabarar fasaha ta wucin gadi.
A lokaci guda kuma, kasar Sin ta sanar da wasu tsare-tsaren da ta ke da su, wato, ta kafa manufa ta zama kasa mafi girma a duniya wajen kera na'urar kera kere-kere a shekarar 2030.
"Abin da zai zama kyakkyawan farawa shi ne ninka kudaden da ake kashewa wajen binciken AI, saboda duk wasu kasashe sun fi Amurka baya kuma suna gab da samun ci gaba a fannin AI", in ji Lee.
Ta hanyar ninka kudaden tallafi ga bincike, zai ninka damar da Amurka za ta samu ta zama babbar hanyar da za ta bi wajen samar da fasaha ta wucin gadi, in ji shi a wata hira da aka yi da kamfanin dillancin labarai na CNBC.
Lee, wanda littafinsa AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order ya fito a wannan watan, wanda Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, babban darektan kamfanin Sinovation Ventures ya shirya.
A shekarun 1980s, ya yi aiki a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon a kan tsarin AI wanda ya yi nasara da mafi kyawun ɗan wasan Othello na Amurka, kuma daga baya ya yi aiki a matsayin memba na Microsoft Research da shugaban kamfanin Google na China.
Lee ya yaba da sakamakon gasar fasaha da gwamnatin Amurka ta yi a baya, ciki har da DARPA Robotics Challenge, kuma ya yi tambaya game da lokacin da za a gudanar da irin wannan taron, saboda wannan lokaci ne na neman sababbin masu tsara makomar.
Lee ya ce, masu bincike a Amirka suna yawan aiki tuƙuru don su samu tallafin gwamnati don yin bincike.
Ba kasar Sin ce ke cinye manyan masana kimiyya ba, manyan kamfanoni ne suka yi hakan.
A cikin 'yan shekarun nan, Facebook da Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun ɗauki manyan jami'o'i da yawa don yin aiki a kan AI.
Lee ya ce, sauye-sauyen da aka yi a manufofin shige da fice na iya taimakawa Amurka wajen samar da fasaha ta wucin gadi.
"Ina ganin ya kamata a ba da katin kore ta atomatik ga duk wanda ke da digiri na biyu a fannin ilimin kere kere", in ji ta.
A watan Yuli na shekarar 2017, majalisar kasar Sin ta sanar da shirinta na bunkasa AI na zamani.
Lee ya bayyana cewa, ko da yake asusun kimiyya na kasar Sin yana ba da tallafi ga ma'aikatan cibiyoyin ilimi kamar yadda National Science Foundation (NSF) da sauran kungiyoyin gwamnati ke ba da kudi ga masu bincike a Amurka, amma ingancin aikin kimiyya a kasar Sin ya kasa.
A wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Haɗin Kai ta Artificial Intelligence don samar da cibiyar haɗin gwiwar masana'antu da masana kimiyya, kuma fadar White House ta sanar da kafa kwamitin da ake kira Select Committee on Artificial Intelligence.
A wannan watan ne DARPA ta zuba jari na dala biliyan biyu a wani shiri da ake kira AI Next,
NSF tana ba da dala miliyan 100 a kowace shekara don tallafawa binciken AI.
