Sanata Elizabeth Warren daga Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar bayan zaben fidda gwani za ta yi la'akari da tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa.
Warren ya sanar a wani taron gari a Holyoke, Massachusetts cewa yana tunanin yin takara.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su shiga cikin Washington su gyara gwamnatin da ke aiki da kyau, kuma lokaci ya yi da mace za ta zama shugaban kasa", in ji Warren a The Hill.
Bayan ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi tunanin takarar shugaban kasa.
A taron birnin, Warren ya soki Donald Trump, ya ce yana ganin yana jan kasar nan zuwa mummunan shugabanci.
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyya", in ji Warren.
Warren ya soki Trump da kuma dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh.
