Kasashe 18 da Washington DC sun goyi bayan sake duba dokokin 'yan gudun hijira
Kasashe 18 da Washington DC sun goyi bayan sake duba sabuwar manufar Amurka ta neman mafaka, wadda ta hana masu guduwa daga 'yan daba da kuma tashin hankali a cikin gida samun mafaka.
Wakilan Majalisar Dokoki daga kasashe 18 da Washington D.C. sun rubuta wasiƙar ƙwararru a Washington a ranar Juma'a don tallafawa wani mai neman mafaka wanda ke kai hari kan manufofin a kotu, in ji NBC News.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai shigar da kara a shari'ar Grace da Sessions ba, wadda kungiyar kare hakkin bil adama ta Amurka ta shigar a watan Agusta kan siyasa ta tarayya.
Mai gabatar da kara ta ce abokin aikinta da 'ya'yan wani gungun masu aikata laifuka sun yi mata mummunan rauni, amma jami'an Amurka sun ƙi karɓar mafakar ta a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An tsare matar a Texas.
Masu gabatar da kara a ƙasashen da ke goyon bayan Grace sun kwatanta El Salvador, Honduras, da Guatemala a matsayin wuraren da ake samun mafaka da yawa daga Amirka domin suna fama da matsalar cin zarafin mutane da kuma yin amfani da mugunta a cikin gida.
Sabuwar manufar Amurka ta 'yan gudun hijira ta soke hukuncin da Hukumar Kula da Shige da Fice (BIA) ta yanke a shekarar 2014 wanda ya bai wa 'yan gudun hijira da ba su da takardun aiki damar neman mafaka daga tashin hankali a cikin gida.
Karl Racine, babban lauyan Washington, D.C., ya bayyana a cikin wata sanarwa a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar manufar ta "yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na jihohi, tarayya da kuma dokokin kasa da kasa".
Dangane da dokar tarayya, duk bukatar neman mafaka dole ne a tantance ta bisa ga hujjoji da kuma yanayin da ake ciki, kuma irin wannan shingen ya saba wa wannan ƙa'idar   da wasiƙar da kwararru suka rubuta.
Masu gabatar da kara sun kuma bayyana a cikin wasikar cewa, manufofin hana shige da fice na cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka, saboda baƙi sun fi saurin zama 'yan kasuwa da kuma cika ayyukan da ke ƙasa.
A watan Yuni, Babban Lauyan Jeff Sessions ya umarci alƙalan da ke kula da batun neman mafaka da kada su ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke fama da tashin hankali a cikin gida da kuma masu aikata laifi.
Damar neman mafaka ta shafi duk wanda ya bar kasarsa saboda tsananin zalunci ko tsoron tsanantawa saboda kabilanci, addini, kasa, kasancewar wani bangare na al'umma ko kuma akidar siyasa  Sessions ya fada a lokacin da ya bayyana manufofinsa a ranar 11 ga watan Yuni.
Ba a ƙirƙiri mafaka don magance matsalolin da mutane ke fuskanta a kowace rana a duk duniya ba, ko da yaya su ke da tsanani.
