Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da yin amfani da tallace-tallace na farfaganda
Jakadan kasar Sin a Amurka ya zargi Beijing da yada farfaganda a jaridar Amurka, mako guda bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wata sanarwa mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke jaddada amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi amfani da wani tallace-tallace da aka buga a China Daily Des Moines Register a ranar Laraba da ta gabata a jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a Iowa, yana zargin China da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka na ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba.
Trump ya zargi Beijing da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka, wasu jami'an Amurka da suka shaida wa Reuters sun ce wannan sabon mataki ne a cikin karfafa kokarin Washington na matsa lamba kan kasar Sin.
Ko da yake ba sabon abu ba ne gwamnatocin ƙasashen waje su yi amfani da tallace-tallace don su ƙarfafa kasuwanci da ƙasarsu, amma akwai yaƙin kasuwanci da ke ci gaba tsakanin Beijing da Washington, inda suke ƙara saka haraji a kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa da su.
Masana a Amurka da China sun ce, a farkon yakin cinikayya, harajin da China ta yi a matsayin martani, ya yi kokarin kai hari kan masu fitar da kayayyaki daga jihohin da Trump da jam'iyyar Republican ke da rinjaye, kamar Iowa.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa mai aiki a lokuta da dama, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikata, manoma da kuma kasuwancin Amurka, saboda jihar Iowa tana fitar da kayayyakin gona da yawa zuwa China.
Branstad ya rubuta a wata kasida a jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi cewa China tana kara lalata kasarmu ta hanyar buga tallace-tallace a cikin jaridarmu mai 'yanci. 
Gwamnatin China na amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin magana da' yan jarida ta hanyar yada farfaganda ta hanyar tallan da aka biya a jaridar Des Moines Register , in ji Branstad.
 Amma idan ka je kantin sayar da jaridu a Beijing, ba za ka samu labarai masu sukar ba. 'Yan jaridar kasar Sin ba su da gaskiya game da ra'ayoyin da ke tsakanin jama'ar kasar Sin game da ci gaban tattalin arzikin kasar Sin, saboda ana sarrafa kafofin watsa labarai sosai ta jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin. 
Branstad ya kara da cewa, wata babbar jarida a kasar Sin ta ki ta fitar da labarinta, amma bai bayyana sunan jaridar ba.
Masu bincike sun ce 'yan Republican za su iya janye mata masu jefa kuri'a daga zaben Kavanaugh kafin zaben tsakiyar shekara.
Masu bincike sun ce, zai iya zama mummunan sakamako ga manyan 'yan siyasa na Republican da ke kare dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh a kan zargin cin zarafin jima'i, musamman ma idan mata suka yi watsi da su kafin zaben.
