Tun kafin Ford ya bayyana a bainar jama'a, manazarta sun yi zaton zai iya ramawa 'yan Republican idan suka ci gaba da goyon bayan zaben Brett Kavanaugh, kuma tun daga wannan lokacin, Ford ya bayyana dalla-dalla a cikin shaidarsa dalilin da ya sa ya zargi dan takarar kotun koli da cin zarafin jima'i.
"Jam'iyyar Republican ta yi kuskure", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin jam'iyyar Republican a NBC News a farkon makon da ya gabata.
