Amma jama'ar Amurka sun rabu a kan ko sun yarda da shaidar Ford ko Kavanaugh, kuma mutane da yawa sun yarda da Kavanaugh fiye da Ford.
A wani sabon binciken da YouGov ya yi, kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun gaskata da shaidar Ford, kuma kashi 35 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun gaskata da shaidar Kavanaugh.
