Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo zai kirkiro sabuwar yanar gizo da za ta yi gogayya da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ta yanar gizo, ya fara farawa don yin gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Aikinsa na baya-bayan nan, Inrupt, wani kamfani ne wanda ya gina kan tsarin budewa na Berners-Lee, Solid.
Tare da Solid, masu amfani za su iya zaɓar inda za su adana bayanan su da kuma wanda zai iya samun damar kowane bayani.
A wata hira da ya yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee yayi barkwanci cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce mamaye duniya.
"Dole ne mu yi shi yanzu", in ji ta game da farawa.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu kantin sayar da kan layi na sirri, wanda aka fi sani da POD.
Wannan zai iya haɗa da jerin abubuwa, jerin abubuwan da za a yi, kalandar, laburaren kiɗa, da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Yana kama da samun Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify a lokaci guda daga wannan burauzar.
Abu na musamman game da bayanan sirri na kan layi shine cewa mai amfani yana da cikakken ikon yanke shawarar wanda zai iya samun damar bayanan sa.
Kamfanin na kiran wannan da aiwatar da 'yancin mutum na yin hukunci akan bayanan mutum.
A cewar John Bruce, shugaban kamfanin Inrupt, aikin kamfanin shi ne samar da albarkatu, matakai da kuma kwarewar da ta dace don tabbatar da cewa kowa yana da damar amfani da Solid.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka kwangila da ke aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Daga wannan makon, masu fasaha a duk duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da aka samo akan shafin Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa tambayar Facebook da Google ko su gabatar da wata fasaha mai kawo sauyi da za ta sauya tsarin kasuwancin kamfanoni gaba daya cikin dare daya.
Ba ma bukatar izini daga gare su.
A wata sanarwa da ya wallafa a shafin Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa aikin Inrupt shine samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma samar da tsarin halittu wanda zai taimaka wajen kare mutuncin da ingancin cibiyar sadarwa da aka gina a Solidra.
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya kawo sauyi a yanar gizo lokacin da ya kafa Cibiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a MIT.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance babban mai tsara ra'ayi a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na Intanet.
Duk da fara Inrupt, Berners-Lee ya ci gaba da zama mai kafa da kuma darektan Cibiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya, Gidauniyar Yanar Gizo da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Buɗe.
"Ina da kwarin gwiwa game da zamanin yanar gizo na gaba".
An yi bikin Bernard Vann, wani limamin coci a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya
Wani limamin Angilika da ya samu lambar yabo ta Victoria Cross a duniya, ya yi bikin cika shekaru 100 da ya yi a Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya.
Mai girma Lt. Colonel Bernard Vann ya samu wannan lambar yabo ne a lokacin da ya kai farmaki a Bellenglise da Lecourt a ranar 29 ga watan Satumba na 1918.
Amma bayan kwana huɗu, wani maharbi ya kashe shi, kuma bai taɓa sanin cewa ya cancanci lambar yabo mafi girma a sojojin Birtaniya ba.
An buɗe dutsen tunawa da shi a ranar Asabar a garin Rushden, a Northamptonshire.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Vann ya ce, yana da ma'ana cewa an ba da wannan dutse ne daidai bayan shekaru 100 da kakansa ya yi aikin da ya cancanci girmamawa.
Jaridar London Gazette ta ce, a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Janar Bernard Vann, wanda shi ne babban jami'in sojan sama, ya ja-goranci rundunarsa ta jirgin ruwa ta hanyar Canal de Saint-Quentin a cikin hazo mai yawa da kuma wuta mai tsanani.
Daga baya, ya yi gaggawar kai hari kuma ya yi gagarumin aikin ja-goranci, bayan haka, ya kai hari kan wani rukunin bindigogi, ya kashe mutane uku.
An kashe Lt. Colonel Bernard Vann a ranar 4 ga watan Oktoba, 1918, a wani harbi da wani dan Jamus ya yi, wata guda kafin a kawo karshen yakin.
"Na san cewa ba zan taɓa yin abin da kakan ya yi ba, kuma hakan ya koya mini tawali'u", in ji Michael Vann, ɗan shekara 72.
Bayan wani zanga-zanga da ƙungiyar matasa ta Brentwood Imperial suka yi, Michael Vann da ɗan'uwansa, Dr. James Vann sun yi wa dutsen tunawa.
Michael Vann ya ce yana jin daɗin taka rawa a bikin, ya kara da cewa: "Gaskiya gwarzo yana nuna ƙarfin hali da yawa suna girmama shi daga baya".
