Fadar White House ta ce za a sake jinkirta ganawar Trump da Rosenstein
Za a iya jinkirta ganawar da ke tsakanin babban lauyan kasar Rod Rosenstein da Donald Trump har na tsawon mako guda, yayin da ake ci gaba da takaddama kan takarar da aka yi wa kotun kolin Amurka, Brett Kavanaugh, a cewar sanarwar da fadar White House ta fitar a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein yana kula da aikin da mai gabatar da kara Robert Mueller ke yi, wanda ke binciken tasirin da Rasha ta yi a zaben, da kuma alakar da ke tsakanin masu ba Trump shawara da gwamnatin Rasha, da kuma yadda Trump ya hana shari'a aiki.
An kwashe watanni ana ta rade-radin ko Trump zai kori mataimakin babban lauyan kasar, wanda hakan zai shafi 'yancin Mueller.
A wannan watan jaridar New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya yi tunanin cewa zai zo taron ne a waya don ya iya rikodin tattaunawar da ya yi da shugaban kasar, kuma ya yi tambaya game da ko za a iya maye gurbin Trump bisa ga Kwaskwarima ta 25.
Rosenstein ya musanta duk abin da ya fada.
Amma a ranar Litinin da ta gabata, ya ziyarci fadar White House, kuma an yi jita-jita cewa zai yi murabus.
Maimakon haka, an ce za su gana da Trump ranar Alhamis, wanda a lokacin zai bayyana a gaban Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a New York.
Trump ya ce yana son sakin Rosenstein amma sai aka dage taron domin kada ya yi karo da sauraron da Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa ya yi, inda Kavanaugh da wata mata da ake zargi da laifin lalata da shi, Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, suka shaida.
A ranar Juma'a, Trump ya ba da umarnin gudanar da binciken FBI na mako guda don bincika zargin da aka yi wa Kavanaugh, wanda hakan ya kara jinkirta zaben majalisar dattijai.
Sakatariyar yada labarai ta Trump, Sarah Sanders, ta kawo ziyara a shirinsa na ranar Lahadi na Fox News.
Lokacin da aka tambaye shi game da taron Rosenstein, ya amsa da cewa: "Ba mu da wata rana a yanzu, ko da a wannan makon, amma ina ganin akwai yiwuwar a sake jinkirta wani mako saboda shari'ar da ke gaban kotun koli.
Ba da daɗewa ba za mu san, kuma kamar yadda na saba, zan sanar da manema labarai.
Wasu 'yan jarida sun yi shakkar wannan sanarwa, saboda Sanders bai yi taron manema labarai a fadar White House ba tun ranar 10 ga watan Satumba.
Mai gabatar da shirin Chris Wallace ya tambaye ni dalilin da ya sa.
Sanders ya amsa cewa rashin taron manema labarai ba don rashin jin daɗin halayyar 'yan jarida ba ne, amma ya kara da cewa: "Ba na jayayya da gaskiyar cewa su masu son jin dadi ne".
Ya kuma yi nuni da cewa za a samu karin ganawa kai tsaye tsakanin Trump da 'yan jarida.
Shugaban ya fi yawan tambayoyin da aka yi masa da ya ce ya yi, kuma ya kara da cewa, ba tare da tabbatar da hakan ba, ya ce, "Mun duba alkaluman".
Sanders ya ce za a ci gaba da samun masu gabatar da labarai, amma idan 'yan jarida sun sami damar yin tambayoyi kai tsaye ga shugaban Amurka, to sun fi kyau da hasken rana fiye da magana da ni.
Muna yawan kokarin samun wannan a cikin jerin, kuma mun samu wasu a cikin makonni da suka gabata, don haka maimakon masu gabatar da labarai na White House, za ku iya magana da shugaban Amurka da kansa.
Trump yakan amsa tambayoyin 'yan jarida a duk lokacin da ya bar fadar White House ko kuma ya halarci taron jama'a ko taron manema labarai tare da manyan baƙi.
Amma taron manema labarai da aka yi shi kaɗai ba safai ake yin hakan ba.
Dalilin hakan, wataƙila, ya fito ne daga abin da ya faru a makon nan, lokacin da shugaban ya yi wani abu na ban mamaki a gaban 'yan jarida a New York.
