Girgizar Kasa da Guguwar Ruwa a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a lokacin da wata girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 15 da guguwa ta afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a.
Har ila yau, an lalata hanyoyin sadarwa a yankin, saboda haka ba a samu wani rahoto daga Donggala ba, wanda ke arewacin Palau, inda girgizar ta auna 7.5.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga birnin Palou.
Ga wasu bayanai masu muhimmanci game da Palus da Donggala a tsibirin Celebes:
Palu babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Celebes ne, wanda ke kan gabar yammacin tsibirin Celebes, a ƙarshen wani ɗan gajeren bakin teku, a cikin 2017 an kiyasta yawan jama'arta 379,800.
A lokacin da aka yi bikin cika shekara 40 da kafa birnin, sai aka yi wata girgizar ƙasa da kuma ambaliyar ruwa.
Gwamnatin Donggala ta fi kilomita 300 a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Celebes.
Gwamnatin  yanki na yanki  yawan jama'a a shekara ta 2017 ya kai kimanin 299 200.
Babban yankin Tsakiyar Tsakiya shine mafi yawan kamun kifi da noma, musamman a yankunan Donggala.
Harkokin hakar ma'adinai na da muhimmanci a tattalin arzikin kasar, amma an fi mayar da hankali ne a Morowali, a gabar tekun Celebes.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta ƙasar Indonesia ta ce a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, a yawancin lokaci, ambaliyar ruwa tana shafan birnin Palut da Donggala.
A shekara ta 1938, ambaliyar ruwa ta halaka mutane fiye da 200 kuma ta halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
A shekara ta 1996, guguwar ruwa ta addabi yankin Donggala ta Yamma, kuma mutane tara sun mutu.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa a cikin Tekun Fasifik.
Wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da kuma ambaliyar ruwa na 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar kasa ta afku a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra, ta haifar da wata guguwa da ta kai kasashe 14, ta kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin wadanda suka mutu a Aceh.
2005: Ƙarƙashin yammacin Sumatra ya yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
An kashe mutane da yawa a tsibirin Nias, kusa da Sumatra.
2006: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta girgiza kudancin tsibirin Java, mafi girma a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ambaliyar ruwa da ta biyo baya ta kashe mutane kusan 700 a gabar teku ta kudu.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta auku a kusa da Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta girgiza tsibirin Mentawai da ke kusa da Sumatra, kuma ta haddasa ambaliyar ruwa mai tsawon kafa 10 a wasu wurare, ta halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ta kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa ta afkawa lardin Aceh Pidie Jaya, ta jawo fargaba da lalacewa da ta tunatar da mutane da yawa game da mummunar ambaliyar ruwa a 2004.
Amma duk da haka, mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a ƙarƙashin gine-ginen da suka rushe.
2018: Wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da ta yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 500 a Lombok, tsibiri da ke da yawan yawon buɗe ido a ƙasar Indonesia.
