Masu gabatar da kara a New York sun nemi a yankewa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa a kan wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci da ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane takwas a birnin New York, wanda ba a taba zartar da hukuncin kisa a jihar ba tun 1953.
