A 'yan makonni bayan harin, an tuhumi Saipov da laifuka 22, ciki har da kisan kai na mataki takwas da aka yi amfani da shi wajen yi wa masu aikata laifuka barazana, da kuma lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci shiri mai kyau da kuma tunanin da ya dace, kuma a cewar su Saipov ya aikata shi ne cikin rashin hankali, zalunci da rashin mutunci.
